ative procedure for higher order approximations\nis detailed. A superconducting instability of the theory is noted at the\nsimplest level with a high transition temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2012 02:47:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Aug 2012 13:56:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 7 Jan 2013 19:36:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 3 Apr 2013 22:51:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-05"}
