bles. We conclude that the expansion of the H II region is also\nleading to the formation of these two young massive embedded YSOs in the\nG8.14+0.23 region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jul 2012 05:54:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
